thread.title: Sophie & Andy
thread.title_full: Victoria Events reviewed by Sophie & Andy

author: Sophie & Andy
title: Sophie & Andy
text: Huge thanks to James for a fantastic service on the Routemaster for our wedding in December - all of our guests had a great time on the bus. James was very responsive to all our emails in the run up to the wedding and the service on the day was great too. The journey up the hills on the way to Stow on the Wold is one we won't forget!
